# Code owners — security-sensitive paths.
#
# GitHub uses this file to assign reviewers automatically when a PR
# touches the matching paths. Until @opollo/security exists as a real
# team, all entries route to @hi (Steven). Add team handles here as
# the company grows.
#
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default — Steven approves everything.
*                                                  @hi

